# Minimal package marker for the sandbox image.
#
# The extractor image bakes ONLY yashigani.documents.bomb_guard (+ this marker
# as the package __init__) so the worker can `import yashigani.documents.bomb_guard`
# WITHOUT importing the full documents package (which pulls the PII detector and
# its heavier deps that are not needed in — and should not be in — the jail).
#
# Do not add imports here: keeping it empty keeps the in-jail surface minimal.
